window.bookSummaryJSON = "<i>New York Times</i> and <i>Washington Post</i> contributor Richard Louv is the widely respected author of seven previous books. In <i>Last Child in the Woods</i>, Louv illustrates how the alienation of today's children from nature can lead to a host of childhood disorders - and he offers effective methods for healing this rift."; 
